           <p>(For) orthodox Christian emperors (and) Greens <note>or</note> (For) Christian emperors ?(and) orthodox Greens</p></div>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>For the epithet Orthodox apparently used of the Greens see also Text 11; Greegoure also restored a reference to the Greens as orthodox in another text at Ephesos, <title>I.Eph.</title> 1192.2, 
               followed by Roueché, 1999, item 9, but in fact the monumental style makes it more likely that the epithet ther refers to the emperors.</p>
